K12D0815_H0772:354a-0: @354a dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12D0815_H0772:354a-1: zas skom bzang po'i ro zhim zhing mdog sdug la dri bsung dang ldan zhing ngad ldang ba /
K12D0815_H0772:354a-2: yon tan phun sum tshogs pas brgyan pa /
K12D0815_H0772:354a-3: dpag bsam gyi shing ljon pa'i nags tshal dkon zhing dri ma med la rgyan gyis klubs pa /
K12D0815_H0772:354a-4: yal ga'i thor to'i ljid kyis gzur za la mgo
K12D0815_H0772:354a-5: lcogs me tog kha phye zhing 'dab mas legs par
K12D0815_H0772:354a-6: brgyan te bung ba lang long khyus lding zhing 'phungs
K12D0815_H0772:354a-7: pa rnams kyis bzhib cing non pa'i shugs kyis bag
K12D0815_H0772:354b-0: tsam @354b 'dar ldem ldem la rin chen yal ga
K12D0815_H0772:354b-1: dang / ma rgad lcug phran gyi bla re 'jol ba dang /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-2: mngon par sgrub par byed pa /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-3: 'gro ba dag tu mtshor bar 'gro ba'i g-yangs chen
K12D0815_H0772:354b-4: po yang ba dag tu mar me snang gsal dag
K12D0815_H0772:354b-5: cing dri ma med pa lta bu byin pa gang
K12D0815_H0772:354b-7: bsod nams kyi rgyu mthun pa dang /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-10: mthun pa bde dgu'i gzhir gyur pa des na sbyin
K12D0815_H0772:354b-11: bdag chen po bdag nyid che ba che ge mo
K12D0815_H0772:354b-12: zhig gi lus dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam gyis
K12D0815_H0772:354b-20: spobs pa phun sum tshogs par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-21: sbyin bdag gi bsod nams ma skyes pa rnams ni skye bar gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-22: sbyin bdag gi longs spyod kyi sa zin ba rnams ni 'phel zhing rgyas par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-23: de bzhin du sbyin bdag gi pha ma mchog tu dka' ba byed byed ba /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-27: bsring bsring la dzambu'i gling bkra yer yer mig gis
K12D0815_H0772:354b-28: mthong bar byed pas kyang bsod nams kyi phud kyi
K12D0815_H0772:354b-29: skal shas thob par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-30: de bzhin du sbyin bdag gi chung ma rnams dang /
K12D0815_H0772:354b-33: sbyin bdag gi gnyen 'dab mdza' bshes rgyas ba'i tshan
K12D0815_H0772:354b-34: ris gang dag 'khod cing 'tshol gnas pa de dag
K12D0815_H0772:354b-35: kyang tshe rang zhing longs spyod che la g-yog 'khor
K12D0815_H0772:355a-1: 'das shing tshe 'phos pa de dag kyang 'gro ba dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-3: gnas tha dad pa'i khyad par thob pa 'gyur te
K12D0815_H0772:355a-4: lha'i gnas su skyes par gyur nas 'phags pa byams
K12D0815_H0772:355a-5: pa'i zhal snga nas mnyes par byed par gyur cig
K12D0815_H0772:355a-6: / de bzhin du rgyal po'i mchog rgyal po chen
K12D0815_H0772:355a-7: po mnga' bdag dam pa dpal lha btsan pos ma
K12D0815_H0772:355a-8: phebs pa rnams ni phebs par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-9: phebs zin pa rnams ni cham du phebs par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-10: stobs kyi 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal srid kyang brnyes par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-11: de bzhin du nye 'khor gyi grong na gnas pa'i rigs bzhi ste bram ze dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-14: dmangs rigs la sogs pa yul gyi mi rnams la nad med cing gnod pa med par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-15: de bzhin du mi mdzed kyi bdag po tshangs pa dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-16: lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-18: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-19: klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-21: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon bde ba'i ri bo dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-24: lnga len la sogs pa dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-27: 'phrog ma bu lnga brgya'i 'khor dang bcas par /
K12D0815_H0772:355a-29: bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa la mngon par dga' ba'i lha dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-5: sbyin bdag gi khyim 'di na gnas pa'i lha rnams dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-6: sbyin bdag gis bsten pa'i lha'i khyad par gyis de dag gzi sbyin dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-8: gzhal med khang rnams rgyas par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-9: de dag gzi byin dang ldan par gyur /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-11: gzhan gyis mi tshugs par gyur /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-12: che bar grags par gyur nas /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-13: sbyin bdag bdag nyid chen po 'di nyid kyi mdzod dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-16: phyugs gdags sna tshogs kyi khyu dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-19: bla 'og gi bya ba thams cad la chos bzhin du bsrung ba dang /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-21: sba ba byed par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-22: gnod pa rnams ni zlog par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-23: don du bsgrubs pa rnams ni snang bar gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-24: de bzhin du sbyin bdag gi dad pa dang sbyar
K12D0815_H0772:355b-25: te dmyal bar skyes pa rnams kyis gnod pa'i sdug
K12D0815_H0772:355b-26: bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-27: dud 'gro rnams gcig la gcig za ba rnams zlog par gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-28: yi dvags kyi bkres shing skoms pa'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-29: mi rnams tshol 'gros g-yen sbyor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:355b-33: rnam par 'jig pa'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:356a-0: mdor na khams gsum du skyes pa'i sems @356a *//
K12D0815_H0772:356a-2: srog chags thams cad kyis kyang mya ngan las 'das pa ma skyes ma byung ba /
K12D0815_H0772:356a-16: mi g-yo ba gang yin pa'i mya ngan las 'das
K12D0815_H0772:356a-17: pa'i chos kyi mchog de reg cing thob par gyur
K12D0815_H0772:356a-18: cig / gnod sbyin gang dag bzhon pa mi zad dpung can lha rdzas gos gyon phreng ba thogs /
K12D0815_H0772:356a-19: gang dag 'jig rten gsum mchog mkhas pa rnams kyis brjod pa'i sangs rgyas skyabs song ba //
K12D0815_H0772:356a-20: lngas rtsen lag na rdo rje nor sbyin dpal can nor bu bzang sras las sogs pa //
K12D0815_H0772:356a-21: de dag thams cad lhan cig rtag tu khyod kyis khyim du chos bzhin srung bar shog /
K12D0815_H0772:356a-22: lngas rtsen dang ni 'phrog ma bu sdug 'khor bcas nor bu bzang sras dbung dang bcas rnams dang //
K12D0815_H0772:356a-23: gnod sbyin dbang po lag na rdo rje rang gi sde tshan bcas dang rang gi sder bcas dang //
K12D0815_H0772:356a-24: gzhan yang gnod sbyin dbang po gang dag sde chen grags ldan bstan pa dag la dga' ba rnams //
K12D0815_H0772:356a-25: thams cad mthun par khyod kyi pha tshan dang ni gnyen sdug bcas la rtag tu skyong gyur cig /
K12D0815_H0772:356a-26: mtshan mo dang ni nyi ma 'char ka nyi ma'i gung rnams dang //
K12D0815_H0772:356b-0: nyi ma nub kar rtag tu khyod la bkra @356b shis ldan par shog /
K12D0815_H0772:356b-1: dpal chen lag na rdo rje nor bu bzang dang 'phags skyes sogs //
K12D0815_H0772:356b-2: khyod dang gnyen 'dun rnams dang bcas la yongs su
K12D0815_H0772:356b-3: skyong gyur cig gtong la dpa' ba rnams kyang khyim
K12D0815_H0772:356b-4: 'khor stobs dang 'byor pa grub cing mi nad med
K12D0815_H0772:356b-5: par shog / yon gnas rnams kyang yon tan tshogs
K12D0815_H0772:356b-6: pas 'phel bar 'gyur zhing 'bru rnams rab tu rgyas
K12D0815_H0772:356b-7: par shog ;mchod rten rnams kyang mchod par 'gyur zhing
K12D0815_H0772:356b-8: bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa yun ring 'bar bar
K12D0815_H0772:356b-9: par shog / shog / rgyal po chos bzhin byed
K12D0815_H0772:356b-10: pas skyong gyur sems can mtha' dag rab zhi bde
